# Mật Lệnh "Rút Tủy Tri Thức"

When the user sends a message containing **"Rút tủy"** or **"rut tuy"** or **"RUT TUY"**, activate this protocol.

## Response Format

Reply with exactly this structure (fill in the blanks based on the most recent code work):

```
RUT TUY TRI THUC — TUMINH_BRAIN
================================
Category    : <one of: Optimization/Safety/Caching/Architecture/Medical Logic/NumPy/Math/NLP>
Pattern     : <short name of the design pattern>
Killer Syntax:
  <3 lines of the most reusable code>
Deep Lesson : <root cause — why this approach wins in 1 sentence>
Tags        : [tag1, tag2, tag3]
================================
[AUTO] Da ghi vao memory/brain_gate.json
```

## Simultaneous Action

At the same time as replying, **write `memory/brain_gate.json`** with the extracted knowledge.

If the gate file already exists (watcher hasn't consumed it yet), read the existing content:
- If it's a single object `{}`, convert to array `[existing, new_entry]`
- If it's already an array `[]`, append the new entry

## Quality Check Before Writing

- `core_syntax` must be actual runnable code, not English description
- `lesson` must state the Big-O or causal reason, not just "it's faster"
- `category` must exactly match the allowed values

## Example Trigger Messages

- "Rút tủy tri thức cho Tuminh_Brain"
- "rut tuy"  
- "Hãy rút tủy đoạn code vừa xong"
- "nap vao brain"
